{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just fell in love with surgery, and this is what I wanted to do, become a surgical nurse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- when I joined the army, I went into the Air Corps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you're young, and you saw all these songs, you know, fly into the sunset.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I figured, well, I'll join the Air Corps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got orders to go to Montgomery, Alabama for six weeks' training, which I did, where we learned about the army, about marching, about what was expected of us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I finished, they asked us what part of the country-- you know, we did have a choice where we would want to go, And I figured, well-- I said, I'd love to go to Florida, thinking maybe I'd get back down to Miami.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Instead, I was sent to Panama City, Florida, on the west coast, Apalachicola.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a gunnery school, and it was a station hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in October of 1943, that's where I went to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the-- this-- to the station hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was called Tyndall Field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, being in the operating room, it really wasn't, you know, that different.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- different operations, maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was very high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The nurses that I met there, and the officers, and even the GIs, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had a blend of everybody, and we all got along very well.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't hear of any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't, you know, realize that there was anything different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite a few of the doctors were Jewish, and some of the GIs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I can recollect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There may have been conversation, but--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
